\begin_layout Standard
This result was obtained after considerable effort.
 We construct an optimization of the phase space GHZ test, such that (a)
 the wavefunctions aren't sharp (no delta functions) and (b) that they disappear
 as 
\begin_inset Formula $q\to\pm\infty$
\end_inset

.
 We consider the same states 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|\psi_{0}\right\rangle ,\left|\psi_{1}\right\rangle $
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $N=2M=8$
\end_inset

, as those considered in 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
