\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi(q)=\left\langle q|\varphi\right\rangle $
\end_inset

 is a localized state, symmetric about 
\begin_inset Formula $q=L/2$
\end_inset

, where 
\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

 is some length scale and 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{n}(q)\equiv\varphi(q-nL)$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $M$
\end_inset

 characterizes the `size' of the state (see 
