\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Although we have not yet discussed the classical limit of BM, as an aside,
 it maybe demonstrated that this indeed follows elegantly.
 If we write 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi=Re^{iS/\hbar}$
\end_inset

 and substitute this in the Schr
